---
// src/components/Products.astro
---
<section id="products" class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12">
            <span class="text-khoalan-yellow font-bold uppercase">Sản Phẩm Của Chúng Tôi</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mt-2">Cung Cấp Giải Pháp Vật Liệu Toàn Diện</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-300 group fade-in-up">
                <div class="overflow-hidden h-56">
                    <img src="https://placehold.co/600x400/ffb400/ffffff?text=Tôn+Lợp" alt="Tôn Lợp" class="w-full h-full object-contain">
                </div>
                <div class="p-6">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Tôn Các Loại</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Cung cấp tôn Hoa Sen, tôn Đông Á, tôn Panel, tôn PU cách nhiệt, tấm nhựa PVC...</p>
                    <a href="#" class="font-bold text-khoalan-yellow hover:underline">Xem chi tiết <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="inline-block h-4 w-4"><line x1="5" x2="19" y1="12" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg></a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-300 group fade-in-up" style="transition-delay: 0.1s;">
                <div class="overflow-hidden h-56">
                    <img src="https://placehold.co/600x400/2a2a2a/ffffff?text=Sắt+Thép" alt="Sắt Thép" class="w-full h-full object-contain">
                </div>
                <div class="p-6">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Sắt Thép Xây Dựng</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Sắt Sendo, sắt Hòa Phát và các loại sắt thép chất lượng cao cho mọi công trình.</p>
                    <a href="#" class="font-bold text-khoalan-yellow hover:underline">Xem chi tiết <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="inline-block h-4 w-4"><line x1="5" x2="19" y1="12" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg></a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-300 group fade-in-up" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">
                <div class="overflow-hidden h-56">
                    <img src="https://placehold.co/600x400/4ade80/ffffff?text=Phụ+Kiện" alt="Phụ Kiện" class="w-full h-full object-contain">
                </div>
                <div class="p-6">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Phụ Kiện Nhà Kính & Xây Dựng</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Nilon Israel, nẹp, ziczac, máng, vít, lề, tay nắm và nhiều phụ kiện khác.</p>
                    <a href="#" class="font-bold text-khoalan-yellow hover:underline">Xem chi tiết <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="inline-block h-4 w-4"><line x1="5" x2="19" y1="12" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section> 